Package org.codice.ddf.migration

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ExportMigrationContext
    The export migration context provides functionality for creating new migration entries for system files and configurations, entries for references in system properties files, and tracking exported migration entries for a given migratable while processing an export migration operation.
    ExportMigrationEntry
    The ExportMigrationEntry interfaces provides support for artifacts that are being exported during migration.
    ImportMigrationContext
    The import migration context keeps track of exported migration entries for a given migratable while processing an import migration operation.
    ImportMigrationEntry
    The ImportMigrationEntry interface provides support for artifacts that are being imported during migration.
    Migratable
    This interface provides the mechanism for implementers to define how their data (e.g.
    MigrationContext
    The migration context is defined as a base interface for all migration contexts.
    MigrationEntry
    The MigrationEntry interface provides support for artifacts that are being exported or imported during migration.
    MigrationMessage
    Interface for describing migration messages that can be recorded during an import or export migration operation.
    MigrationReport
    The migration report provides information about the execution of a migration operation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MigrationInformation
    Class that provides information status for migration operations.
    MigrationSuccessfulInformation
    Special informational message providing successful information about a migration operation.
    MigrationWarning
    Class that provides warning statuses for migration operations.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MigrationOperation
    Defines various migration operations.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    MigrationException
    Exception that indicates some problem with the migration operation.
